\p
\v 1 \add This letter is from\add* Paul, a prisonerВҰ140603 of \nd messiahВҰ140604 Yeshua\nd*, and our brotherВҰ140609 TimothyВҰ140607. \add I'm writing\add* to our dear co-worker PhilemonВҰ140610,
