\v 3 \add May youВҰ140633 all experience\add* graceВҰ140632 and peaceВҰ140635 from ourВҰ140639 fatherВҰ140638 \nd GodВҰ140637\nd* and from the \nd masterВҰ140641 Yeshua\nd* \add the\add* \nd messiahВҰ140643\nd*.
\s1 Paul's prayer and gratefulness
