\p
\v 4 \add Philemon,\add* I'm alwaysВҰ140648 thankingВҰ140644 my \nd GodВҰ140646\nd* and mentioningВҰ140649 youВҰ140650 in my prayersВҰ140654
\v 5 \add after\add* hearingВҰ140656 your faithВҰ140662 and about your loveВҰ140659 for the \nd masterВҰ140668 YeshuaВҰ140669\nd* and for all the believers.
\v 6 \add I pray thatВҰ140687\add* the fellowshipВҰ140677 of yourВҰ140680 faithВҰ140679 may becomeВҰ140682 activeВҰ140681 in the knowledgeВҰ140684 of everyВҰ140685 goodВҰ140686 thing in us towardВҰ140691 \add the\add* \nd messiahВҰ140692\nd*, [WHAT DOES THAT MEAN???]
\v 7 because I was very happy and encouraged by yourВҰ140705 loveВҰ140704, because the heartsВҰ140708 of the believers have been refreshedВҰ140711 by you, brotherВҰ140714.
\s1 Paul's request to Philemon concerning Onesimus
\rem /s1 A Request for Onesimus; Paul's Plea for Onesimus; Paul's Appeal for Onesimus; A runaway slave
\p
\v 8 ThereforeВҰ140715, with the help of the \nd messiahВҰ140718\nd*, I would be brave enough to tell you what you need to do,
\v 9 butВҰ140738 becauseВҰ140725 of loveВҰ140728 as PaulВҰ140734, an olderВҰ140735 manВҰ140735 andВҰ140738 now also a prisonerВҰ140740 for \nd Yeshua\nd* the \nd messiahВҰ140741\nd*, I'm just going to encourage youВҰ140730 to do it.
\v 10 \x + \xo 10: \xt Col 4:9.\x*So I'm going to encourage youВҰ140745 concerning OnesimusВҰ140757 who became my \add spiritual\add* вҖҳsonвҖҷ since I've been imprisoned.
\v 11 Before, he was uselessВҰ140761 to you, butВҰ140766 now he's usefulВҰ140768 to both of us.
\p
\v 12 I sentВҰ140770 himВҰ140774 to youВҰ140772 (even though in my heartВҰ140779
\v 13 I wanted to keep him \add here\add*) so that he might be servingВҰ140791 me \add here due to\add* the bondsВҰ140795 of the goodВҰ140797 messageВҰ140797,
\v 14 but I didn'tВҰ140807 want to doВҰ140805 anything without \add hearing\add* yourВҰ140813 opinionВҰ140802, so that you're not doing goodВҰ140812 because you have to, but rather because you want to.
\p
\v 15 It was possiblyВҰ140818 becauseВҰ140820 of that that heВҰ140822 was separatedВҰ140822 \add from you\add* for a while, so that on the eternalВҰ140826 \add scale\add* you could fullyВҰ140828 accept himВҰ140827,
\v 16 no longerВҰ140829 as a slave, but better than a slaveвҖ”a dear brother to me most of all, but preferably \add also\add* to youвҖ”a brother in the bodyВҰ140845 and in \nd YahwehВҰ140848\nd*.
\p
\v 17 ThereforeВҰ140850, if you consider me as your partnerВҰ140853, accept himВҰ140855 like you'd accept me,
\v 18 butВҰ140859 if heВҰ140861 didВҰ140861 anything wrongВҰ140861 to you or owes you anything, charge it to me.
\v 19 \sig I, PaulВҰ140870, wroteВҰ140871 this bit in my own handwriting. I will pay back anything \+add he owes you\+add*, then I won'tВҰ140878 need to be reminding you that you \+add pretty much\+add* owe yourselfВҰ140883 to me.\sig*
\v 20 \sig Yes, brotherВҰ140889, \+add with both of us being\+add* in \+nd YahwehВҰ140894\+nd*, I mightВҰ140892 \+add hopefully\+add* benefitВҰ140892 from youВҰ140891вҖ”refreshВҰ140895 myВҰ140896 heartВҰ140898 in \+add the\+add* \+nd messiahВҰ140900\+nd*.\sig*
\p
\v 21 \sig I wroteВҰ140906 to you because I was sure that you'd obey \+add my request\+add*, in fact knowingВҰ140908 that you'd do even more than what I ask.\sig*
\s1 Paul's final greetings
\p
\v 22 \sig \+add Go ahead andВҰ140917\+add* prepareВҰ140919 somewhere for me to stay, becauseВҰ140923 I'm hopingВҰ140922 that I'llВҰ140929 be able to visit, \+add thanks\+add* to you all praying \+add for me\+add*.\sig*
\rem /s1 Paul's Final Greetings; Final Greetings and Benediction
\v 23 \x + \xo 23: \xt Col 1:7; 4:12.\x*\sig EpafrasВҰ140934, myВҰ140937 fellowВҰ140936 prisoner in \+nd YeshuaВҰ140940\+nd* the \+nd messiahВҰ140939\+nd*, sends his greetingsВҰ140931\sig*,
\v 24 \x + \xo 24: a \xt Acts 12:12,25; 13:13; 15:37-39; Col 4:10; \xo b \xt Acts 19:29; 27:2; Col 4:10; \xo c \xt Col 4:14; 2Tim 4:10; \xo d \xt Col 4:14; 2Tim 4:11.\x*\sig as do myВҰ140947 fellow-workers Mark, AristarchusВҰ140942, DemasВҰ140943, and LukeВҰ140944.\sig*
\p
\v 25 \sig \+add May\+add* the graceВҰ140949 of ourВҰ140952 \+nd masterВҰ140951\+nd* \+nd Yeshua\+nd* the \+nd messiahВҰ140954\+nd* be with the spiritВҰ140957 of youВҰ140958 all \+add there\+add*. May itВҰ140959 be soВҰ140959.\sig*
